      "writtenOn": "2020-04-02T12:09:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Pretty much, yes.  I\u0027m planning to leave the RepoManager interface around.  I think all of the existing implementations can be split up into Parent and Child, but I can imagine having a situation where the parent and child are so closely related that it just doesn\u0027t make sense to split them, so I\u0027ll leave that possibility open to avoid having to jump through unnecessary hoops.",
